query:
SELECT 
  (SELECT id FROM restaurants LIMIT 1) as correct_restaurant_id,
  (SELECT restaurantId FROM recipes WHERE name = 'Test Shrimp Recipe') as recipe_restaurant_id,
  (SELECT restaurantId FROM ingredients WHERE name = 'Test Shrimp') as ingredient_restaurant_id;
